text: Takatoshi Iwatsuki (born 29 November 1964) is a Japanese rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Japan Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan Category:Medalists at the 1994 Asian Games
